5. Async UI: loading + error + empty states.
6. Primary actions: expo-haptics on press.

NAV TABS (6): Today · Bible · Community · Quest · Events · Profile.

FREEMIUM: respect premium gates for AI, Quest play, group plans, soundscapes, events hosting — use a central paywall trigger/store when implementing gates.

Match existing project patterns: ThemeProvider, fonts (Playfair/Nunito/DM Sans until Lora migration), file structure under app/ and src/, and **Bun** for installs/scripts (`bun install`, `bunx expo`, never npm/npx for this repo).
